org.jpokemon.pmapi.pokemon.nature
Class ClassicNatures

java.lang.Object
  org.jpokemon.pmapi.pokemon.nature.ClassicNatures

public final class ClassicNatures
extends Object

Defines the 25 classic natures (personalities) that a Pokémon may possess.

Note that this class is final. If you want to add or remove natures, it cannot be extended; you must write your own lookup class.

Since:
Alpha
Author:
Atheriel
